-   <span data-ttu-id="8472e-421"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakStarted>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8472e-421"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakStarted>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8472e-422">Wywoływane, gdy Syntezator rozpoczyna się generowanie mowy.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8472e-422">Raised when the synthesizer begins generating speech.</span></span>  
  
